Package: rigakuXRD
Type: Package
Title: X-Ray Diffraction Data Analysis Package for Rigaku Data Sets
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: person("Thomas", "Gredig", email = "tgredig@csulb.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre","cph"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5824-7626"))
Maintainer: Thomas Gredig <tgredig@csulb.edu>
Description: Imports x-ray diffraction data and assists with the 
  x-ray data analysis. It supports several data file formats for 
  import and provides tools to find and fit spectra peaks.
